issue.title: Search Engine API (for query categorization):
issue.body:
- `Index::search(String query)` returns a list of categories ranked by most relevant 
- `Index::Index(List<Document> docs)` (the constructor) will index the list of documents. 

```java
class Document {
    String category
    List<String> keywords
}
```
